"n. 老年糊涂；溺爱 【英】 n. 老年糊涂(senility) ；溺爱(foolish or excessive affection) n. 老糊涂(由于大脑功能的衰老) = senility; 溺爱 【记】dote溺爱, 到了溺爱小孙子的年龄－老糊涂 【记】音：到+ age，到年纪了，老了 dotage (n.)  ""the state of one who dotes,"" c.1300; see dote + -age. Originally of all sorts of mental impairment, not just that resulting from old age. First recorded late 14c. for ""senility."""
